&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lecture Material for this week:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Slides: Monopoly Pricing - Part I &lt;a href=&quot;https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&amp;amp;id=1lz0arnrdjyPgNB9dsqSneRjKB1VGy4VL&quot;&gt;PDF&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
